| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5763 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: bdac0afc-d2ad-5d19-9ca5-6ce4bd54ecf6"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
